.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, dubstep, punk, reggae
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, lacrosse, basketball, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
4. the fan of dubstep is the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the fan of punk is between the fan of metal and the fan of dubstep##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | punk           | metal | reggae  |
| Sport         | swimming | biathlon | lacrosse   | basketball |

