.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, country, indie, trance
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, taxi, quad-bike
1. the fan of country is the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the fan of metal##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the fan of metal is between the person driving the boat and the fan of indie##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | country | metal | indie      |
| Transport     | taxi | boat    | jet-ski  | quad-bike |

