.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, golf, cricket, cycling
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, trike, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the van is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person driving the trike is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person driving the scooter##2
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the van is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | swimming | cycling | cricket     | golf   |
| Transport   | scooter   | trike     | ship | van |

