.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, freelancer, mechanic, accountant
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, jet-ski, bus
1. the mechanic is between the person driving the car and the musician##2
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the musician##1
3. the accountant is on the right of the musician##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the musician is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | freelancer | mechanic | musician | accountant |
| Transport   | car         | bus       | snowmobile    | jet-ski         |

