.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, orange, peas, raspberry
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, golf, cycling, badminton
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person eating peas##1
3. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating orange##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the person eating orange and the person who's sport is badminton##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | raspberry   | peas      | orange   | corn  |
| Sport   | badminton | golf | cycling | skiing |

