.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, broccoli, avocado, kiwi
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, family, horror, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person eating broccoli is between the person eating kiwi and the person eating pomegranate##2
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | pomegranate     | broccoli | kiwi   | avocado        |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | horror   | family | spy |

