.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, reading, photography, dancing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, jazz, d&b
1. the fan of jazz is the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
3. the fan of folk is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the fan of hip-hop is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | reading | photography | dancing | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | jazz          | hip-hop     | d&b  | folk     |

