.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, german, indonesian, indian
4 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, ferret, horse
1. the australian is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the indian is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the mouse and the german##2
4. the owner of the horse is the owner of the horse##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | indian | german | australian | indonesian |
| Pet           | ferret  | horse  | hedgehog | mouse      |

