.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, spanish, nigerian, egyptian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, snowboarding, cycling, cricket
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the egyptian is the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is between the thai and the nigerian##2
5. the nigerian is the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | thai   | spanish | nigerian |
| Sport         | handball | snowboarding | cricket     | cycling    |

