.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, baking, puzzles, reading
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, rat, horse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the owner of the dog and the person who's hobby is reading##2
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | reading     | fishing | baking |
| Pet     | mouse | horse | rat       | dog     |

 